Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.59,0:01:03.75,Drrr Default,tanaka,0000,0000,0000,,I'm starting to see more yellow people recently.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.75,0:01:04.87,Drrr Default,setton,0000,0000,0000,,The Yellow Napkins?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.87,0:01:08.29,Drrr Default,kanraku,0000,0000,0000,,Have you heard that The Slasher is actually the act of Dollars?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.29,0:01:10.79,Drrr Default,yellow,0000,0000,0000,,We're really not the same without you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.79,0:01:12.25,Drrr Default,izaya,0000,0000,0000,,How's he doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.25,0:01:14.17,Drrr Default,haruna,0000,0000,0000,,He visits me from time to time.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.17,0:01:15.17,Drrr Default,haruna,0000,0000,0000,,He was just out there.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.17,0:01:17.37,Drrr Default,shingen,0000,0000,0000,,Tokyo's air is ugly.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.37,0:01:18.80,Drrr Default,shingen,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you agree?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.80,0:01:22.53,Drrr Default,mamba,0000,0000,0000,,Parasite! Parasite! Parasite!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.03,0:01:52.75,Drrr Default,kanraku,0000,0000,0000,,Did you hear?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.75,0:01:56.84,Drrr Default,kanraku,0000,0000,0000,,Some students from Raira Academy were just attacked by The Slasher.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.54,0:01:58.80,Drrr Default,tanaka,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.80,0:02:00.64,Drrr Default,setton,0000,0000,0000,,That's scary.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.64,0:02:02.68,Drrr Default,kanraku,0000,0000,0000,,I'm totally, frickin' serious.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.68,0:02:05.18,Drrr Default,kanraku,0000,0000,0000,,Female freshmen, apparently.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.18,0:02:06.21,Drrr Default,tanaka,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.21,0:02:08.85,Drrr Default,tanaka,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna idle while I make some calls.{ROM means Read Only Member}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.85,0:02:10.51,Drrr Default,kanraku,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.51,0:02:12.27,Drrr Default,kanraku,0000,0000,0000,,It wasn't your girlfriend.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.93,0:02:15.02,Drrr Default,tanaka,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.02,0:02:17.07,Drrr Default,tanaka,0000,0000,0000,,But I'm still concerned.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.35,0:02:20.30,Drrr Default,setton,0000,0000,0000,,Do you know where it happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.30,0:02:21.48,Drrr Default,kanraku,0000,0000,0000,,Well,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.48,0:02:25.63,Drrr Default,kanraku,0000,0000,0000,,it's just a little past Higashi Ikebukuro station, along the Metro Highway.{http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Shuto_Expressway}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.63,0:02:30.06,Drrr Default,kanraku,0000,0000,0000,,You won't have any problems finding it, since there are police cruisers and such there.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.58,0:02:31.75,Drrr Default,setton,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.15,0:02:35.28,Drrr Default,setton,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, I'm going AFK for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.28,0:02:37.51,Drrr Default,kanraku,0000,0000,0000,,Setton-san, are you going over there to gawk?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.76,0:02:40.26,Drrr Default,kanraku,0000,0000,0000,,Aw, darn.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.73,0:02:42.76,Drrr Default,tanaka,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, I'm gonna sign off too.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.60,0:02:45.01,Drrr Default,kanraku,0000,0000,0000,,Did you get a hold of her?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.01,0:02:47.35,Drrr Default,tanaka,0000,0000,0000,,She said she's at the police station now...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.35,0:02:49.89,Drrr Default,tanaka,0000,0000,0000,,I guess she witnessed it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.89,0:02:51.60,Drrr Default,tanaka,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna go.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.50,0:02:53.62,Drrr Default,kanraku,0000,0000,0000,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.62,0:02:54.88,Drrr Default,kanraku,0000,0000,0000,,Then, me too.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.05,0:03:09.42,Drrr Thoughts,celty,0000,0000,0000,,The Slasher.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.21,0:03:15.29,Drrr Thoughts,celty,0000,0000,0000,,At that point, I was completely unaware that this bloody incident
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.00,0:03:24.43,Drrr Thoughts,celty,0000,0000,0000,,had a strong tie to a girl's destiny, and to my past.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.77,0:03:37.48,Drrr Default,shinra,0000,0000,0000,,I'm home!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.53,0:03:47.95,Drrr Default,shinra,0000,0000,0000,,I'm home.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.33,0:03:49.87,Drrr Default,shinra,0000,0000,0000,,Hello, hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.34,0:03:57.04,Drrr Default,shinra,0000,0000,0000,,I'm home, Celty!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.89,0:04:02.20,Drrr Default,shingen,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome home, dear.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.06,0:04:08.32,Drrr Default,celty,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.74,0:04:11.02,Drrr Default,shinra,0000,0000,0000,,I witnessed a horrifying sight.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.63,0:04:15.50,Drrr Default,celty,0000,0000,0000,,A horrifying sight?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.50,0:04:17.28,Drrr Default,shinra,0000,0000,0000,,Don't make me say it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.28,0:04:18.48,Drrr Default,shinra,0000,0000,0000,,I want to forget about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.48,0:04:20.81,Drrr Default,shingen,0000,0000,0000,,Man, that felt good.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.81,0:04:24.46,Drrr Default,shinra,0000,0000,0000,,You should at least take that white thing off when you're in the shower.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.46,0:04:25.17,Drrr Default,shingen,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.17,0:04:29.38,Drrr Default,shingen,0000,0000,0000,,Tokyo's air is dirty, so I can't ever take it off.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.38,0:04:33.42,Drrr Default,shingen,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, Celty-kun, thank you for last night.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.42,0:04:37.28,Drrr Default,shingen,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, what's up with those rude guys wearing yellow?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.28,0:04:39.59,Drrr Default,shinra,0000,0000,0000,,That must be the Yellow Napkins.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.59,0:04:42.82,Drrr Default,shinra,0000,0000,0000,,They formed around the time you left for America.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.35,0:04:47.97,Drrr Default,shinra,0000,0000,0000,,I thought they were laying low after that fight with the Blue Squares.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.72,0:04:52.77,Drrr Default,shingen,0000,0000,0000,,They can all die in the sewer after fighting each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.77,0:04:54.61,Drrr Default,celty,0000,0000,0000,,Stop asking the impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.61,0:05:00.27,Drrr Default,shinra,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, Celty brought you home safely, so pay her.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.88,0:05:02.25,Drrr Default,shingen,0000,0000,0000,,I'll keep a tab with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.25,0:05:04.03,Drrr Default,shinra,0000,0000,0000,,I absolutely refuse.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.92,0:05:07.49,Drrr Default,shingen,0000,0000,0000,,Then I'll just ignore it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.03,0:05:12.91,Drrr Default,shingen,0000,0000,0000,,I was just testing you, Celty-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.27,0:05:15.13,Drrr Default,shingen,0000,0000,0000,,If you free me right now...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.13,0:05:16.39,Drrr Default,shingen,0000,0000,0000,,Ouch! Ouch!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.39,0:05:17.57,Drrr Default,shingen,0000,0000,0000,,It's poking me!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.57,0:05:19.91,Drrr Default,shingen,0000,0000,0000,,The tip of the shadow is poking me!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.91,0:05:21.04,Drrr Default,shingen,0000,0000,0000,,Shinra!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.04,0:05:24.13,Drrr Default,shingen,0000,0000,0000,,I'm in a real crisis!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.04,0:05:29.70,Drrr Default,shingen,0000,0000,0000,,I certainly expect my son to know how to act in such a situation!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.70,0:05:31.00,Drrr Default,shinra,0000,0000,0000,,Of course I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.19,0:05:38.78,Drrr Default,celty,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for your business.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.76,0:05:42.93,Drrr Default,shingen,0000,0000,0000,,I will not be leaving any inheritance to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.93,0:05:44.62,Drrr Default,shinra,0000,0000,0000,,I don't need any.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.07,0:05:48.82,Drrr Default,shingen,0000,0000,0000,,You've been tricked by that monster.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.22,0:05:53.22,Drrr Default,shinra,0000,0000,0000,,If Celty's tricked me and stolen my soul, that's what I really want anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.12,0:05:57.17,Drrr Default,shingen,0000,0000,0000,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.17,0:06:00.33,Drrr Default,shingen,0000,0000,0000,,Oh wow, wow, wow, what, Celty-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.33,0:06:03.30,Drrr Default,shingen,0000,0000,0000,,Have you fallen in love with Shinra?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.92,0:06:09.32,Drrr Default,shingen,0000,0000,0000,,I knew my son was weird enough to develop feelings for you,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.32,0:06:11.46,Drrr Default,shingen,0000,0000,0000,,but now you love Shinra too?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.64,0:06:13.74,Drrr Default,celty,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.41,0:06:15.52,Drrr Default,shinra,0000,0000,0000,,Celty!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.00,0:06:19.27,Drrr Default,shinra,0000,0000,0000,,It's great that you admit your feelings for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.63,0:06:23.63,Drrr Default,shinra,0000,0000,0000,,Our relationship used to be so vague and opaque,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.63,0:06:29.65,Drrr Default,shinra,0000,0000,0000,,but now we're super close to each other and ready to go public with the news!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.65,0:06:32.16,Drrr Default,shinra,0000,0000,0000,,This progress makes me want to jump up and down in joy!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.16,0:06:33.13,Drrr Default,celty,0000,0000,0000,,You're embarrassing me!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.13,0:06:34.20,Drrr Default,celty,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up already!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.20,0:06:37.50,Drrr Default,shinra,0000,0000,0000,,Now I'm overjoyed that I confessed my love to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.45,0:06:43.07,Drrr Default,shingen,0000,0000,0000,,Did you think I'd allow this relationship?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.07,0:06:44.00,Drrr Default,celty,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.00,0:06:52.03,Drrr Default,shingen,0000,0000,0000,,Are you aware that you are an uninvited member of human society, better known as a "monster"?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.03,0:06:53.18,Drrr Default,celty,0000,0000,0000,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.18,0:06:55.18,Drrr Default,shingen,0000,0000,0000,,"Of course"? Wait...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.18,0:06:57.96,Drrr Default,celty,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong with that?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.10,0:07:04.49,Drrr Default,shingen,0000,0000,0000,,Seems like my plan to get control of the situation by pointing out my opponent's anti-social status failed.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.49,0:07:07.69,Drrr Default,celty,0000,0000,0000,,That's not convincing at all, coming from you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.69,0:07:08.92,Drrr Default,celty,0000,0000,0000,,Besides...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.99,0:07:14.85,Drrr Default,celty,0000,0000,0000,,Shinra told me that he likes me just the way I am now!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.41,0:07:18.10,Drrr Default,shingen,0000,0000,0000,,Fine, I'll allow this relationship.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.08,0:07:22.14,Drrr Default,shingen,0000,0000,0000,,But, from now on, you are...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.13,0:07:24.96,Drrr Default,shingen,0000,0000,0000,,to address me as "Father."
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.96,0:07:25.84,Drrr Default,celty,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.95,0:07:30.01,Drrr Default,shingen,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, Celty-kun,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.01,0:07:33.43,Drrr Default,shingen,0000,0000,0000,,you can't regain your memories if you don't regain your head.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.43,0:07:38.61,Drrr Default,shingen,0000,0000,0000,,That is, the memories of your time as a Dullahan with a head in Ireland, your homeland.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.19,0:07:42.06,Drrr Default,celty,0000,0000,0000,,That... can't be helped.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.69,0:07:48.90,Drrr Default,shinra,0000,0000,0000,,Let's make many new memories together to make up for your lost ones.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.11,0:07:51.24,Drrr Default,celty,0000,0000,0000,,Shinra...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.69,0:07:54.38,Drrr Default,shinra,0000,0000,0000,,To start, let's have a wedding.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.38,0:08:00.45,Drrr Default,shinra,0000,0000,0000,,I want to get your measurements for the wedding dress, so take off that shadow suit.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.75,0:08:06.08,Drrr Default,shingen,0000,0000,0000,,This reminds me: he's always been a strange kid. Always happy whenever there's a dissection.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.37,0:08:08.30,Drrr Default,celty,0000,0000,0000,,It's clearly because of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.30,0:08:10.59,Drrr Default,shingen,0000,0000,0000,,Call me "Father"!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.13,0:08:18.50,Drrr Default,shingen,0000,0000,0000,,I told you not minutes ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.50,0:08:19.55,Drrr Default,shingen,0000,0000,0000,,How careless of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.55,0:08:22.64,Drrr Default,shingen,0000,0000,0000,,This is why you didn't even notice when I stole your head.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.60,0:08:27.15,Drrr Default,shingen,0000,0000,0000,,Oh crap!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.15,0:08:29.90,Drrr Default,celty,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-Wh-Wh-What did you just say?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.90,0:08:31.05,Drrr Default,shingen,0000,0000,0000,,What do I do now?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.05,0:08:33.93,Drrr Default,shingen,0000,0000,0000,,I accidentally let slip a very important secret.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.93,0:08:35.22,Drrr Default,shingen,0000,0000,0000,,But it'll be okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.22,0:08:38.05,Drrr Default,shingen,0000,0000,0000,,Celty is a klutz, so you'll never catch on.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.91,0:08:40.82,Drrr Default,shingen,0000,0000,0000,,Klutzy Celty!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.82,0:08:42.50,Drrr Default,shingen,0000,0000,0000,,Klutzy Celty!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.68,0:08:42.50,Drrr Override,celty,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.50,0:08:43.41,Drrr Default,celty,0000,0000,0000,,And don't repeat it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.72,0:08:48.46,Drrr Default,shingen,0000,0000,0000,,I can easily predict the attacks of an angry klutz!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.16,0:08:52.37,Drrr Default,shinra,0000,0000,0000,,Even you won't get away if you make fun of Celty.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.07,0:08:54.04,Drrr Default,shingen,0000,0000,0000,,All right! All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.04,0:08:55.24,Drrr Default,shingen,0000,0000,0000,,I'll explain everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.90,0:08:58.19,Drrr Default,shingen,0000,0000,0000,,I guess there's no use hiding it anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.19,0:09:04.26,Drrr Default,shingen,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, the one who stole your head and gave it to a pharmaceutical company was me!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.26,0:09:05.51,Drrr Default,celty,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be shameless about it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.51,0:09:06.68,Drrr Default,shingen,0000,0000,0000,,Fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.68,0:09:08.03,Drrr Default,shingen,0000,0000,0000,,Then come with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.03,0:09:09.50,Drrr Default,shingen,0000,0000,0000,,There's something I want to show you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.96,0:09:23.33,Drrr Default,shinra,0000,0000,0000,,What? He ran away?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.61,0:09:28.68,Drrr Default,celty,0000,0000,0000,,That fucking bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.68,0:09:29.54,Drrr Default,celty,0000,0000,0000,,I won't let him!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.17,0:09:40.21,Drrr Default,shingen,0000,0000,0000,,Is she gone?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.24,0:09:47.48,Drrr Default,shingen,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like my trick of only pressing the elevator's button succeeded.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.87,0:09:49.57,Drrr Default,shingen,0000,0000,0000,,I'll come get my bags later.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.57,0:09:50.48,Drrr Default,shingen,0000,0000,0000,,See ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.74,0:10:00.67,Drrr Default,celty,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it, where'd he go?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.32,0:10:08.83,Drrr Default,mikado,0000,0000,0000,,Celty-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.26,0:10:10.74,Drrr Default,celty,0000,0000,0000,,Is something wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.74,0:10:12.38,Drrr Default,celty,0000,0000,0000,,You're totally spaced out.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.26,0:10:15.35,Drrr Default,mikado,0000,0000,0000,,I was thinking about things.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.02,0:10:17.12,Drrr Default,celty,0000,0000,0000,,Tell me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.39,0:10:19.93,Drrr Default,celty,0000,0000,0000,,What's on your mind?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.93,0:10:21.22,Drrr Default,celty,0000,0000,0000,,You look gloomy.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.76,0:10:26.12,Drrr Default,mikado,0000,0000,0000,,It's about The Slasher.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.12,0:10:29.72,Drrr Default,mikado,0000,0000,0000,,There's this strange rumor spreading on the Net.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.72,0:10:31.21,Drrr Default,celty,0000,0000,0000,,Strange rumor?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.21,0:10:35.43,Drrr Default,mikado,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, saying that The Slasher is the work of the Dollars.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.43,0:10:36.36,Drrr Default,celty,0000,0000,0000,,No way.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.75,0:10:38.84,Drrr Default,celty,0000,0000,0000,,Do you really believe that?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.84,0:10:41.18,Drrr Default,mikado,0000,0000,0000,,I don't, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.71,0:10:47.25,Drrr Default,mikado,0000,0000,0000,,But if the rumor takes off, something dangerous might happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.25,0:10:52.38,Drrr Default,mikado,0000,0000,0000,,There's already a lot of tension between the Dollars and the Yellow Napkins.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.78,0:10:59.38,Drrr Thoughts,celty,0000,0000,0000,,It's true that the town's balance is fragile right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.01,0:11:05.44,Drrr Default,celty,0000,0000,0000,,Mikado, I'll check around about The Slasher too.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.44,0:11:06.93,Drrr Default,mikado,0000,0000,0000,,Celty-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.28,0:11:09.01,Drrr Default,celty,0000,0000,0000,,So get going.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.01,0:11:13.74,Drrr Default,celty,0000,0000,0000,,People like you are easy targets if you space out in a place like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.65,0:11:16.05,Drrr Default,mikado,0000,0000,0000,,That's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.78,0:11:18.35,Drrr Default,mikado,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.63,0:11:23.33,Drrr Default,shizuo,0000,0000,0000,,The Slasher, huh...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.17,0:11:26.41,Drrr Default,shizuo,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, but I don't have a clue.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.41,0:11:27.95,Drrr Default,celty,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.31,0:11:33.24,Drrr Default,shizuo,0000,0000,0000,,You don't have to go so far for the Dollars.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.24,0:11:35.46,Drrr Default,celty,0000,0000,0000,,It's not just for the Dollars.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.02,0:11:39.80,Drrr Default,celty,0000,0000,0000,,I have some history with her.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.61,0:11:46.09,Drrr Default,celty,0000,0000,0000,,I'd be dead if I had a head.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.09,0:11:47.38,Drrr Default,shizuo,0000,0000,0000,,You dumbass...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.01,0:11:52.82,Drrr Default,shizuo,0000,0000,0000,,I know the one who says, "Dumbass," is the dumbass, but I'm fine being a dumbass, so I'll say it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.82,0:11:53.73,Drrr Default,shizuo,0000,0000,0000,,You dumbass!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.73,0:11:55.16,Drrr Default,shizuo,0000,0000,0000,,You should've told me that first!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.16,0:11:56.30,Drrr Default,shizuo,0000,0000,0000,,I'll kill her!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.30,0:11:57.47,Drrr Default,shizuo,0000,0000,0000,,Totally kill her!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.47,0:11:58.44,Drrr Default,shizuo,0000,0000,0000,,Surely kill her!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.73,0:12:00.48,Drrr Default,shizuo,0000,0000,0000,,Fucking seriously kill her!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.48,0:12:03.68,Drrr Default,celty,0000,0000,0000,,But you know, I'm a headless rider.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.68,0:12:05.17,Drrr Default,celty,0000,0000,0000,,I'm totally fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.17,0:12:06.56,Drrr Default,shizuo,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.56,0:12:08.86,Drrr Default,shizuo,0000,0000,0000,,That's not the issue here anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.86,0:12:12.21,Drrr Default,shizuo,0000,0000,0000,,Attacking you deserves a million deaths.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.21,0:12:16.33,Drrr Default,shizuo,0000,0000,0000,,Killkillkillkillkill...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.70,0:12:14.97,Drrr Override,celty,0000,0000,0000,,What about work?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.97,0:12:16.33,Drrr Override,celty,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't you on break right now?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.33,0:12:18.03,Drrr Default,shizuo,0000,0000,0000,,I don't care.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.03,0:12:22.49,Drrr Default,celty,0000,0000,0000,,I won't allow you to get fired on my account.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.49,0:12:27.15,Drrr Default,celty,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, I need more information before I look for The Slasher.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.15,0:12:29.83,Drrr Default,celty,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go get ready, so wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.82,0:12:33.85,Drrr Default,shizuo,0000,0000,0000,,Fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.85,0:12:37.69,Drrr Default,shizuo,0000,0000,0000,,But do it ASAP.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.69,0:12:41.15,Drrr Default,shizuo,0000,0000,0000,,Killkillkillkillkillkill...{SATSUGAI, SATSUGAI SE YO...}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.15,0:12:45.82,Drrr Thoughts,celty,0000,0000,0000,,There was a reason I needed to be away from Shizuo.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.79,0:12:55.00,Drrr Default,izaya,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so glad you came to see me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.00,0:12:58.10,Drrr Default,izaya,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, did you find your head yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.56,0:13:00.41,Drrr Default,celty,0000,0000,0000,,Forget about the head.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.41,0:13:02.57,Drrr Default,celty,0000,0000,0000,,Let me get straight to the point.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.57,0:13:04.72,Drrr Default,celty,0000,0000,0000,,I want info about The Slasher.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.72,0:13:06.76,Drrr Default,izaya,0000,0000,0000,,Three big ones will do.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.20,0:13:15.84,Drrr Default,izaya,0000,0000,0000,,So your clothes and wallet are both made of shadows.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.84,0:13:21.22,Drrr Default,izaya,0000,0000,0000,,So, if a really bright light shone on you, would you be buck naked?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.22,0:13:22.86,Drrr Default,celty,0000,0000,0000,,Are you interested?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.86,0:13:24.44,Drrr Default,izaya,0000,0000,0000,,Nah.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.44,0:13:32.37,Drrr Default,izaya,0000,0000,0000,,Unlike the weirdo quack and student, I don't get aroused by the headless or a head.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.86,0:13:39.06,Drrr Default,celty,0000,0000,0000,,I'm fine, but if you insult Shinra again, I won't forgive you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.86,0:13:42.46,Drrr Default,izaya,0000,0000,0000,,You're so in love.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.28,0:13:52.77,Drrr Default,izaya,0000,0000,0000,,But if another Dullahan comes and tempts him, he might easily fall for her.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.77,0:13:55.24,Drrr Default,celty,0000,0000,0000,,I want to believe that he wouldn't...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.24,0:13:56.49,Drrr Default,celty,0000,0000,0000,,But even if that happens...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.49,0:13:58.69,Drrr Default,izaya,0000,0000,0000,,Would you kill Shinra, then kill yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.69,0:14:00.11,Drrr Default,celty,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.11,0:14:04.69,Drrr Default,celty,0000,0000,0000,,I just won't let any other headless woman come near him.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.30,0:14:08.21,Drrr Default,celty,0000,0000,0000,,Because I love him right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.81,0:14:13.63,Drrr Default,izaya,0000,0000,0000,,You've grown so similar to a human!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.63,0:14:16.82,Drrr Default,izaya,0000,0000,0000,,But you should be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.82,0:14:26.37,Drrr Default,izaya,0000,0000,0000,,The closer you come to being human, the bigger the shock you'll get when you regain your head.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.37,0:14:29.88,Drrr Default,celty,0000,0000,0000,,I'll worry about that after I get my head back.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.32,0:14:35.19,Drrr Default,celty,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, I'm starting to think that I might not need the head.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.19,0:14:36.55,Drrr Default,celty,0000,0000,0000,,Putting that topic aside,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.55,0:14:38.89,Drrr Default,celty,0000,0000,0000,,tell me about The Slasher.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.89,0:14:41.62,Drrr Default,celty,0000,0000,0000,,I paid you, so don't tell me you don't have anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.40,0:14:44.23,Drrr Default,izaya,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.23,0:14:48.57,Drrr Default,izaya,0000,0000,0000,,I have some killer info that I haven't leaked to the police, media, or Internet yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.57,0:14:51.39,Drrr Default,izaya,0000,0000,0000,,I was actually waiting to tell you first.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.39,0:14:52.82,Drrr Default,celty,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.97,0:14:57.59,Drrr Default,izaya,0000,0000,0000,,Because this case involves supernatural evil spirits.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.01,0:15:00.67,Drrr Default,izaya,0000,0000,0000,,Have you heard about a sword named "Saika"?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.67,0:15:01.83,Drrr Default,celty,0000,0000,0000,,"Saika"?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.83,0:15:07.60,Drrr Default,izaya,0000,0000,0000,,This might sound unbelievable, but Saika is a cursed sword that actually existed in Shinjuku.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.60,0:15:09.15,Drrr Default,celty,0000,0000,0000,,A cursed sword?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.15,0:15:11.18,Drrr Default,celty,0000,0000,0000,,Like Muramasa?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.18,0:15:14.26,Drrr Default,izaya,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, it's a sword with a mysterious power.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.27,0:15:18.62,Drrr Default,shinra,0000,0000,0000,,What's on your mind?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.62,0:15:22.64,Drrr Default,celty,0000,0000,0000,,I heard a story about a cursed sword named Saika.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.64,0:15:28.40,Drrr Default,celty,0000,0000,0000,,Apparently, there's a legend that says Saika has a mind of its own, and that it can take control of humans.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.40,0:15:34.90,Drrr Default,celty,0000,0000,0000,,And each victim of The Slasher testified that The Slasher had red eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.71,0:15:38.18,Drrr Default,shinra,0000,0000,0000,,And you think that's because of Saika?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.18,0:15:39.03,Drrr Default,celty,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.62,0:15:45.29,Drrr Default,celty,0000,0000,0000,,Every night there was a slasher incident, someone with the username "Saika" logged onto the Internet.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.00,0:15:52.30,Drrr Default,celty,0000,0000,0000,,But when I got attacked by her before, I didn't notice her presence coming toward me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.87,0:15:57.39,Drrr Default,celty,0000,0000,0000,,If Saika isn't human, I would've sensed her presence.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.09,0:16:00.67,Drrr Default,shinra,0000,0000,0000,,Saika only takes over the mind of a person.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.67,0:16:03.31,Drrr Default,shinra,0000,0000,0000,,And that person is actually moving around.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.07,0:16:08.21,Drrr Default,shinra,0000,0000,0000,,So it's possible that there isn't a presence that you can detect.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.21,0:16:12.07,Drrr Default,celty,0000,0000,0000,,You know a lot about Saika...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.07,0:16:15.90,Drrr Default,shinra,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, you know, you asked me to check on it before.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.90,0:16:18.39,Drrr Default,shinra,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, come to bed soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.88,0:16:26.83,Drrr Thoughts,celty,0000,0000,0000,,That made me think that Shinra was hiding something from me...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.10,0:16:38.22,Drrr Default,shingen,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, welcome back!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.22,0:16:44.57,Drrr Default,shingen,0000,0000,0000,,Ever since Nebula took over Yagiri Pharmaceutical, I've been researching Miss Namie's whereabouts.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.57,0:16:48.50,Drrr Default,shingen,0000,0000,0000,,Then I found her frequenting your room.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.50,0:16:53.05,Drrr Default,shingen,0000,0000,0000,,So I threatened her with this toy gun to get in.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.05,0:16:54.38,Drrr Default,namie,0000,0000,0000,,A toy gun?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.38,0:16:56.47,Drrr Default,shingen,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't I tell you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.63,0:17:00.26,Drrr Default,namie,0000,0000,0000,,Shouldn't we turn this guy over to the police?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.26,0:17:04.33,Drrr Default,shingen,0000,0000,0000,,But wouldn't you be the one who gets in trouble?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.33,0:17:10.11,Drrr Default,shingen,0000,0000,0000,,If they search the way I tell them to, they'll find a young woman's head in the room!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.68,0:17:15.65,Drrr Default,shingen,0000,0000,0000,,You know, that might become the new headline that replaces The Slasher.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.65,0:17:20.35,Drrr Default,izaya,0000,0000,0000,,So Shinra's twisted character comes from you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.35,0:17:22.10,Drrr Default,shingen,0000,0000,0000,,Praising me won't get you anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.38,0:17:26.79,Drrr Default,shingen,0000,0000,0000,,But seriously, I don't need to have the head right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.76,0:17:34.61,Drrr Default,shingen,0000,0000,0000,,My corporation is quite surprised from seeing Celty-kun's manner on TV.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.43,0:17:40.70,Drrr Default,shingen,0000,0000,0000,,So they came to the conclusion that they should study the body before the head.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.70,0:17:46.21,Drrr Default,shingen,0000,0000,0000,,So now I'm the one who's supposed to be searching for the head.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.21,0:17:51.99,Drrr Default,shingen,0000,0000,0000,,It seems you have a very interesting plan for the head.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.99,0:18:00.24,Drrr Default,shingen,0000,0000,0000,,You assume that a Valkyrie is a Dullahan, and thus are trying to wake the head up by placing it within a conflict.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.24,0:18:03.32,Drrr Default,shingen,0000,0000,0000,,That's a very unique idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.32,0:18:05.99,Drrr Default,izaya,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I'm trying different things.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.99,0:18:10.48,Drrr Default,izaya,0000,0000,0000,,In the worst case scenario, I might have to take it somewhere that has an armed conflict.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.95,0:18:15.49,Drrr Default,izaya,0000,0000,0000,,I'd appreciate it if we can cooperate.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.04,0:18:17.20,Drrr Default,shingen,0000,0000,0000,,Very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.20,0:18:19.70,Drrr Default,shingen,0000,0000,0000,,I've had eyes on you for a while too.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.70,0:18:24.64,Drrr Default,shingen,0000,0000,0000,,There's no one around me who's willing to run an experiment based on a mythical legend.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.64,0:18:26.75,Drrr Default,shingen,0000,0000,0000,,Including me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.75,0:18:28.37,Drrr Default,izaya,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.41,0:18:30.69,Drrr Default,shingen,0000,0000,0000,,Now...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.69,0:18:32.70,Drrr Default,shingen,0000,0000,0000,,Let me give you some advice.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.70,0:18:40.88,Drrr Default,shingen,0000,0000,0000,,If you're trying to provoke Celty-kun's head or soul by causing a pseudo-conflict here in Tokyo,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.88,0:18:43.97,Drrr Default,shingen,0000,0000,0000,,don't get her involved in someone else's conflict.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.97,0:18:46.97,Drrr Default,shingen,0000,0000,0000,,Instead, getting everyone else involved...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.66,0:18:51.94,Drrr Default,shingen,0000,0000,0000,,in a disaster with her in the middle would be the way to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.30,0:18:55.91,Drrr Default,izaya,0000,0000,0000,,That's my intent.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.03,0:19:01.45,Drrr Default,izaya,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, things are progressing faster than I anticipated.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.93,0:19:04.93,Drrr Default,nasujima,0000,0000,0000,,Anri!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.99,0:19:09.93,Drrr Default,nasujima,0000,0000,0000,,You're able to help with the sports festival preparations already?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.93,0:19:10.81,Drrr Default,anri,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.81,0:19:12.49,Drrr Default,nasujima,0000,0000,0000,,I was so worried about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.49,0:19:15.94,Drrr Default,nasujima,0000,0000,0000,,Why were you with those slashed students?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.94,0:19:18.30,Drrr Default,nasujima,0000,0000,0000,,Were they picking on you again?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.95,0:19:20.25,Drrr Default,nasujima,0000,0000,0000,,I'm worried.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.25,0:19:22.18,Drrr Default,nasujima,0000,0000,0000,,I'm very worried.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.18,0:19:25.38,Drrr Default,nasujima,0000,0000,0000,,The Slasher might come after you again.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.38,0:19:26.88,Drrr Default,nasujima,0000,0000,0000,,It's not safe to walk alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.88,0:19:28.81,Drrr Default,kida,0000,0000,0000,,Harassing her again?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.81,0:19:30.81,Drrr Default,kida,0000,0000,0000,,Tsk, tsk, Sensei.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.11,0:19:33.79,Drrr Default,nasujima,0000,0000,0000,,I was concerned about Anri.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.79,0:19:35.46,Drrr Default,kida,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, you call her by her given name.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.46,0:19:36.82,Drrr Default,kida,0000,0000,0000,,How risqué!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.80,0:19:43.37,Drrr Default,kida,0000,0000,0000,,If you pay too much attention to her, she might transfer schools like Niekawa-senpai.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.79,0:19:46.82,Drrr Default,kida,0000,0000,0000,,You were her homeroom teacher last year, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.82,0:19:48.76,Drrr Default,kida,0000,0000,0000,,Of Niekawa Haruna-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.96,0:19:51.00,Drrr Default,anri,0000,0000,0000,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.40,0:19:53.29,Drrr Default,nasujima,0000,0000,0000,,Do you know Niekawa?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.29,0:19:54.97,Drrr Default,kida,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, but just her name.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.43,0:19:58.55,Drrr Default,kida,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, us students should leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.05,0:20:03.49,Drrr Default,anri,0000,0000,0000,,Who is Niekawa Haruna-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.05,0:20:05.49,Drrr Default,kida,0000,0000,0000,,Hey Anri,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.05,0:20:09.93,Drrr Default,kida,0000,0000,0000,,Mikado hasn't confessed his love to you yet, has he?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.93,0:20:10.59,Drrr Default,anri,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.59,0:20:12.06,Drrr Default,kida,0000,0000,0000,,Just as I thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.06,0:20:15.35,Drrr Default,kida,0000,0000,0000,,But you {\i1}are{\i0} aware that he's fallen head-over-heels for you, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.95,0:20:19.12,Drrr Default,anri,0000,0000,0000,,Ryugamine-kun is a good friend of mine, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.81,0:20:24.31,Drrr Default,kida,0000,0000,0000,,It seems my best friend is seriously in love with you,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.31,0:20:27.02,Drrr Default,kida,0000,0000,0000,,so I'll watch from the sidelines for now.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.02,0:20:31.46,Drrr Default,kida,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, I need be on good terms with all the fair ladies of the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.46,0:20:32.87,Drrr Default,mikado,0000,0000,0000,,Masaomi!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.87,0:20:35.12,Drrr Default,mikado,0000,0000,0000,,Sonohara-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.12,0:20:38.13,Drrr Default,kida,0000,0000,0000,,Here comes The Timid.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.13,0:20:39.87,Drrr Default,mikado,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, did you wait long?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.87,0:20:42.32,Drrr Default,kida,0000,0000,0000,,The wait was so long, I thought I was turning into a fossil.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.32,0:20:43.90,Drrr Default,mikado,0000,0000,0000,,Uh... Square root of three points.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.90,0:20:44.66,Drrr Default,kiha,0000,0000,0000,,"Square root"?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.66,0:20:46.15,Drrr Default,kiha,0000,0000,0000,,Why square root?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.15,0:20:49.47,Drrr Default,kiha,0000,0000,0000,,Give me an easier score to understand, like -20 points!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.47,0:20:50.49,Drrr Default,kida,0000,0000,0000,,Bye!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.49,0:20:51.97,Drrr Default,mikado,0000,0000,0000,,See you tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.97,0:20:53.48,Drrr Default,anri,0000,0000,0000,,See you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Drrr Default,yellownapkins,0000,0000,0000,,{mumbling}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.70,0:21:13.25,Drrr Default,haruna,0000,0000,0000,,You finally came.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.71,0:21:26.70,Drrr Default,shinra,0000,0000,0000,,Celty.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.53,0:21:30.75,Drrr Default,shinra,0000,0000,0000,,It's about Saika.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.75,0:21:33.93,Drrr Default,shinra,0000,0000,0000,,My father owned it for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.59,0:21:38.43,Drrr Default,shinra,0000,0000,0000,,But he sold it to an antique dealer a few years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.43,0:21:39.52,Drrr Default,celty,0000,0000,0000,,Shingen did?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.95,0:21:41.02,Drrr Default,celty,0000,0000,0000,,For what?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.02,0:21:44.78,Drrr Default,shinra,0000,0000,0000,,Saika is known as a sword that cuts the soul.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.17,0:21:47.32,Drrr Default,celty,0000,0000,0000,,Does that mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.32,0:21:48.69,Drrr Default,shinra,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.69,0:21:52.57,Drrr Default,shinra,0000,0000,0000,,He used Saika to steal your head.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.57,0:21:55.68,Drrr Default,shinra,0000,0000,0000,,To cut the soul that ties the head and the body.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.05,0:22:01.11,Drrr Default,celty,0000,0000,0000,,And you've known about this the whole time?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.11,0:22:02.10,Drrr Default,shinra,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.10,0:22:06.84,Drrr Default,shinra,0000,0000,0000,,I learned later that he used it to steal your head.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.55,0:22:12.08,Drrr Default,shinra,0000,0000,0000,,I thought I could tell you this now, since you're trying to forget about your head.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.54,0:22:13.68,Drrr Default,shinra,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.98,0:22:17.52,Drrr Default,celty,0000,0000,0000,,Let me think about this alone for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.80,0:22:24.34,Drrr Default,shinra,0000,0000,0000,,Just as I thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.40,0:22:27.72,Drrr Thoughts,celty,0000,0000,0000,,Love creates confusion.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.72,0:22:32.91,Drrr Thoughts,celty,0000,0000,0000,,That same night, the cursed sword Saika was trying to love a certain girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.91,0:22:37.41,Drrr Thoughts,celty,0000,0000,0000,,The girl who couldn't discover her place in this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.70,0:22:39.67,Drrr Thoughts,celty,0000,0000,0000,,Sonohara Anri.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.27,0:24:16.18,Drrr Default,preview,0000,0000,0000,,Ikebukuro...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.93,0:24:19.18,Drrr Default,preview,0000,0000,0000,,I was only looking...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.61,0:24:23.34,Drrr Default,preview,0000,0000,0000,,For the energy source of this town packed with junk.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.34,0:24:26.57,Drrr Default,preview,0000,0000,0000,,For the truth behind the town of ever-increasing desire.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.57,0:24:29.65,Drrr Default,preview,0000,0000,0000,,Next time - A Fool's Good Advice.
